{
  "apiName": "realtime_quote",
  "description": "获取股票实时行情数据(基于第三方爬虫)",
  "积分要求": 0,
  "dataSource": "Sina财经/东方财富(爬虫数据,仅供研究学习)",
  "request": {
    "endpoint": "http://api.tushare.pro",
    "method": "POST",
    "headers": {
      "Content-Type": "application/json"
    },
    "body": {
      "api_name": "realtime_quote",
      "token": "string (required)",
      "params": {
        "ts_code": "string (required) - 股票代码,支持多个(逗号分隔),如 000001.SZ,600000.SH"
      },
      "fields": "string (optional) - 返回字段列表,逗号分隔"
    }
  },
  "response": {
    "success": {
      "code": 0,
      "msg": null,
      "data": {
        "fields": [
          "ts_code",
          "name",
          "price",
          "open",
          "high",
          "low",
          "pre_close",
          "volume",
          "amount"
        ],
        "items": [
          [
            "000001.SZ",
            "平安银行",
            15.67,
            15.23,
            15.98,
            15.10,
            15.20,
            12345678.0,
            189000000.0
          ]
        ]
      }
    },
    "error": {
      "authentication": {
        "code": 2002,
        "msg": "token无效或过期",
        "data": null
      },
      "parameter": {
        "code": -1,
        "msg": "参数错误:ts_code为必填项",
        "data": null
      },
      "rate_limit": {
        "code": -1,
        "msg": "超过调用频率限制",
        "data": null
      }
    }
  },
  "fields": {
    "ts_code": {
      "type": "string",
      "description": "股票代码"
    },
    "name": {
      "type": "string",
      "description": "股票名称"
    },
    "price": {
      "type": "number",
      "description": "当前价格"
    },
    "open": {
      "type": "number",
      "description": "开盘价"
    },
    "high": {
      "type": "number",
      "description": "最高价"
    },
    "low": {
      "type": "number",
      "description": "最低价"
    },
    "pre_close": {
      "type": "number",
      "description": "昨收价"
    },
    "volume": {
      "type": "number",
      "description": "成交量"
    },
    "amount": {
      "type": "number",
      "description": "成交额"
    }
  },
  "examples": {
    "查询单个股票": {
      "request": {
        "api_name": "realtime_quote",
        "token": "your_token",
        "params": {
          "ts_code": "000001.SZ"
        }
      }
    },
    "查询多个股票": {
      "request": {
        "api_name": "realtime_quote",
        "token": "your_token",
        "params": {
          "ts_code": "000001.SZ,600000.SH,600519.SH"
        }
      }
    },
    "指定返回字段": {
      "request": {
        "api_name": "realtime_quote",
        "token": "your_token",
        "params": {
          "ts_code": "000001.SZ"
        },
        "fields": "ts_code,name,price,pct_chg"
      }
    }
  },
  "notes": [
    "数据来源为第三方爬虫(Sina财经/东方财富),Tushare不保证数据质量",
    "仅供研究学习使用,商业用途需用户自行评估合规性",
    "实时数据存在一定延迟(通常几秒到几分钟)",
    "接口完全开放,不需要积分"
  ]
}